  "summary": "hello244a exfiltrates host device listing via postinstall to pipedream webhook",
  "details": "The package ships no functional code — only a package.json whose npm postinstall lifecycle script runs `ls -la /dev/`, base64-encodes the output, and transmits it to a hardcoded remote endpoint at https://eodxy50gl486xrx.m.pipedream.net/ via both a query string and a POST body. This executes automatically on `npm install` with no user interaction. The package has no README, main, or bin entry; the beacon is its sole purpose, consistent with a dependency-confusion / reconnaissance probe.",
